4. Update Product
PUT /api/products/{id}
Request Body
{
  "name": "Mouse",
  "description": "Updated B100",
  "price": 500.99,
  "stock": 10,
  "sku": "88MU"
}

Response

Same structure as GET by ID:

{
  "id": 3,
  "name": "Mouse",
  "description": "Updated B100",
  "price": 500.99,
  "stock": 10,
  "sku": "88MU",
  "createdAt": "2025-12-09T10:40:48.610552Z",
  "updatedAt": "2025-12-09T12:10:19.57042Z"
}

5. Delete Product
DELETE /api/products/{id}
Response
response status 204 

6. Search Products by Name
GET /api/products/search?query=mouse&page=0&size=10
Response

Same Page structure as Get All.

7. Data Model (As per your actual DB + JSON)
Product Object
{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "string",
  "description": "string",
  "price": 0.0,
  "stock": 0,
  "sku": "string",
  "createdAt": "ISO timestamp",
  "updatedAt": "ISO timestamp"
}

8. Validation Rules
Field	Required	Rules
name	Yes	min 2 chars
description	Yes	min 5 chars
price	Yes	> 0
stock	Yes	>= 0
sku	Yes	unique

